Summary: Witness saw object while driving towards Sacramento on I-5 in June,1991.
trends: There have been 83 other sightings in Sacramento
There were no other sightings in Sacramento on or around June 15th 1991
divs: Sighting Details Witness contacted MUFON in regards to a complex, unnatural mark that she found on her body (photo to be attached). It appeared and then disappeared;the cause of the mark is unknown. She has experienced a number of unusual events throughout her lifetime, including a UFO sighting in 1991. It is highly unlikely that particular event is related to the recent mark. The witness, who wishes to remain anonymous, has also submitted a picture of the mark to www.AAARC.US.
